label: ABC_hP6_186_b_b_a-003
title: LiGaGe Crystal Structure
comments:
This is the ternary form of the \href{current_web_home_dir/AB2_hP6_186_b_ab-001}{$C27$ (CdI$_{2}$) structure}. 
 The choice of the origin of the $z$-axis in space group $P6_{3}mc$ \#186 is arbitrary, we use the values given by (Bockelmann, 2012). 
 We have attempted to list the ``other compounds'' so that the (2a) atom is first, but do not guarantee that we are always correct.
